{"type": "article", "id": 30054, "title": "袜子包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-24T22:51:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160724231740YcpZwsdnTeLH36af.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>茶、香蕉、舌头、窗户，你能想象这些其实是袜子品牌的包装吗？<a href=\"http://hyelalee.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chris + Jessie</a> 是美国设计师 Hyela Lee 创作的概念品牌，四种生活中常见的物品都作了特别的镂空设计，露出一部分色彩斑斓的袜子。Lee 希望通过这种出人意料的组合为平凡的日用品注入趣味，就好像品牌的标语那样：socks for fun。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016072423234895GM0e8FrBlN47gz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232348YbZrmawvpWh1xzIV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160724232348RnruZH2yXOiQlVg4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607242323483umHAO9VGMRLP41d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}